Class StudentGraph

java.lang.Object
StudentGraph
public class StudentGraph extends Object
Reference for a Student Graph This class represents a graph of university students, where each student is a node and edges represent connections between students. The graph is implemented using an adjacency list. Author: Cooper Nelson
